scapeMCMC 1.1-2 (2011-02-09)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o No user-visible changes.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
scapeMCMC 1.1-1 (2010-09-05)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Minor improvements in help pages.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
scapeMCMC 1.1-0 (2010-09-04)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Added argument 'col.strip' to plotDens() and plotTrace(), with gray as
  default.

o Changed default 'cex.axis' in plotDens() to 0.8.

o Reduced clutter at startup.

o Added two vignettes: dsc-vignette.pdf and gallery.pdf.

o Updated URLs and email address.




